<paragraph blockId="7.[813,1456,567,752]" pageId="7" pageNumber="448">
The genus was reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[1135,1295,598,624]" name="French Guiana" pageId="7" pageNumber="448">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
as 
<taxonomicName authority="Bigot, 1857" authorityName="Bigot" authorityYear="1857" class="Florideophyceae" family="Rhodomelaceae" genus="Pachychaeta" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ceramiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="448" phylum="Rhodophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1331,1455,598,624]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="448">Pachychaeta</emphasis>
Bigot, 1857
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="TOMASOVIC G." box="[984,1194,630,656]" pageId="7" pageNumber="448" pagination="85 - 90" refId="ref15515" refString="TOMASOVIC G. 2002 a. - Resume sur la connaissance des Asilidae (Diptera Brachycera) de Guyane francaise et description de trois especes nouvelles. Bulletin de la Societe royale belge d'Entomologie 138: 85 - 90." type="journal article" year="2002">Tomasovic (2002a)</bibRefCitation>
. Currently this genus is considered a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Papavero, 2009)" baseAuthorityName="Papavero" baseAuthorityYear="2009" box="[1082,1355,662,688]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Lecania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="448" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1082,1163,662,687]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="448">Lecania</emphasis>
(Papavero, 2009)
</taxonomicName>
. Furthermore, no information concerning species name or collecting site was provided (specimens not examined).
